On December 9 , <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">the British firm Tesco</COREF> said hello to consumers in <COREF ID="15" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> when <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">it</COREF> formally opened <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> clean , bright and spacious store .
