Shocking the world
The performance of these large retailers in <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">Taiwan</COREF> has been startling , and superstore chains from Holland , France , the United States and <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT">Britain</COREF> have been arriving on <COREF ID="4" TYPE="IDENT">these shores</COREF> one after another .
